{"tid":1979342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（回帶）李顯龍談香港：五大訴求旨在「羞辱拖垮港府」 不為解決社會問題","createTime":"2020-04-19T11:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T11:17:57.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e7fa2a5785168933496f119f688d5ee8434164b5","tid":1979342,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T11:00:59.000Z","msg":"香港《逃犯條例》反修例風波不息，香港特首林鄭月娥發表施政報告、美國眾議院通過《香港人權與民主法案》之際，新加坡總理李顯龍罕有公開評論香港問題。李顯龍批評，香港示威者「五大訴求缺一不可」主張，不是為了解決香港社會問題，反而旨在羞辱和推翻特區政府。<br />\n<br />\n外電報道，新加坡總理李顯龍周三（16日）在當地，出席福布斯全球行政總裁會議（Forbes Global CEO Conference）時談及香港問題。李顯龍稱：<br />\n<br />\n示威者強調五大訴求，缺一不可，但這些訴求並不旨在解決香港問題。這些訴求旨在羞辱和拖垮政府。<br />\n<br />\n（The demonstrators say they have five major demands and not one can be compromised but those are not demands which are meant to be a program to solve Hong Kong's problems. Those are demands which are intended to humiliate and bring down the government.）<br />\n<br />\n李顯龍表示，香港問題並無簡單解決辦法，而示威者想要普選，只是香港並非國家，而是一個特別行政區；香港秩序或許可以以改革立法機關和社會政策來恢復，但這並不易辦。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，一國兩制是香港面臨問題之一，需要以開放的思維處理（progressively tackled）：<br />\n<br />\n精簡地說，對中國內地而言，不能只想着一國，也需要記住兩制；對香港而言，不能只想着兩制，也需要記住一國。<br />\n<br />\n（To put it very neatly, from China's point of view, they must not only think of one country but remember this is two systems; and from Hong Kong's point of view, you must not only think of two systems but remember that this is one country.）<br />\n<br />\n李顯龍又指，香港亂局為整個地區都帶來了喧鬧，產生不良影響：<br />\n<br />\n當香港遇上麻煩，出現示威甚至暴動時，當香港特首在立法會遭到喝罵而退場時，我認為這對香港是件悲傷的事，對整個地區亦有壞影響。我們擔憂地注視着。<br />\n<br />\n（When Hong Kong is troubled, when there are demonstrations or worse riots, when the chief executive is booed out of the Legislative Council chamber, I think that is very sad for Hong Kong and bad for the region. We look on with concern.）<br />\n<br />\n李顯龍強調，新加坡並不希望企業從香港遷去獅城，反而希望香港局勢平息下來，企業能夠安穩地在港經營：<br />\n<br />\n地區穩定才最適合新加坡興旺發展，其他地方昌盛，新加坡亦可和他們做生意。<br />\n<br />\n（We thrive best in Singapore when the region is stable, when other countries are prospering and we can do business with them.）<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2476473</code></pre>"},{"pid":"af191c9925e4fdb233010f89b85e7b8eb73279e0","tid":1979342,"uid":58552,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T11:03:26.000Z","msg":"中国新加坡省猴城<br />\n特首 嗶坡猴"},{"pid":"8dd703b9f196d4807a9bd9cf92d28e4c2a4c2ab2","tid":1979342,"uid":35087,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T11:03:55.000Z","msg":"都唔知關佢咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4737b70f29d7c9e989e94b384e3b35b9f1e84665","tid":1979342,"uid":207247,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8dd703b9f196d4807a9bd9cf92d28e4c2a4c2ab2","tid":1979342,"uid":35087,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T11:03:55.000Z","msg":"都唔知關佢咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T11:04:34.000Z","msg":"m s m d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e3fcb43788dbff95b3b6145ad24ec409a5eba29","tid":1979342,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T11:05:24.000Z","msg":"monkey country monkey sick"},{"pid":"ea5b62e92ad6946f41cb3e978678fe6eee924341","tid":1979342,"uid":73565,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4737b70f29d7c9e989e94b384e3b35b9f1e84665","tid":1979342,"uid":207247,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8dd703b9f196d4807a9bd9cf92d28e4c2a4c2ab2","tid":1979342,"uid":35087,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T11:03:55.000Z","msg":"都唔知關佢咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T11:04:34.000Z","msg":"m s m d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T11:06:02.000Z","msg":"Monkey: So tired leh. Don't wanna see, Don't wanna do lah"},{"pid":"13